1. *Izađeš* iz sobe da vidiš šta se dešava vani. (You come out of the room to see what's going on outside.)

2. On je *izašao* ranije da bi obavio nešto. (He left earlier to do something.) 

3. *Izađeš* li večeras sa nama? (Are you coming out with us tonight?)

4. Ona je *izašla* iz kuće pre nego što je stigao. (She left the house before he arrived.)

5. *Izađoše* iz kuće u isto vreme. (They left the house at the same time.) 

6. On je *izlazio* van svakog dana. (He was going out every day.)